呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb01a6b2f2df3aa72717655a0b3c9738e2f64448","tid":1538571,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:56.000Z","msg":"班狗不嬲condom 仔 宜家佢地仲有利用價值先無事 到佢地無利用價值 就係審判既開始"},{"pid":"067aa453120e2d4ac36265055ff21be1d0340212","tid":1538571,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"而家個問題已經唔係徹完就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9789f90908d56d2b7b7ab416ed683eeeaa3c7f","tid":1538571,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割？撤回都唔割！"},{"pid":"96cd83a618859e753ddd4f2a0758d45096cca502","tid":1538571,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"好燃好笑 依家見到 黑警 好似見到恐怖分子 一樣 雞飛狗走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db28db0645c5484aac31a388728f9a40e40233d2","tid":1538571,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"condom狗準備定還眼還手都得<br />\n<br />\n等到人權民主法案出埋<br />\n你班仆街淨係去到中國北韓伊朗"},{"pid":"73070a8806e78bfa